      "raw_text": "The case of Thomas FNn OF\nPortland, charged in the United\nStates court with fraudulently OBJ\ntanning land under the homestead\nact, came to close last night and\nafter arguments by the attorneys\nJudge Whitson took the papers\nand will announce his decision\nlater.\n\n\n1t was claimed Flyn had SIT\nacres of land at the time he took\nup his homestead and that he deed\ned his wife 100 acres just before\nhe filed his claim for the purpose\nof evading the law. Flyn denies\nthe governments contention and\nsays he made the deed in good\nfaith."
